<br>
Lol, you took my arguement , WIzel, but then you are not a caster and don't se all of teh iplications.<br>
<br>
First of all:<br>
<br>
Wizards are the WEAKEST casters from level 1 to say level 44/49.<br>
Necros and Mages perfom WAAAAY better, soloing and in a group. No one can dispute this. Mages even rival our nukes at certain level and outnuke us (Lv 34, 39, 44).<br>
<br>
Let alone Chanters. (IMMENSE grouping/raiding power).<br>
<br>
Now this changes a little at level 51. Level 51 to 60 were released in teh Kunark era and Verant realized after some months, that the classes WIzard/Mage are just too close to each other, with the Mage seriously outdoing the Wizard.<br>
<br>
So the typical role of the Wizard as a raiding class became evn more extreme, Wizel. Of course nowadays you'll see Wizards quad kiting. there has been said a lot about quad kiting.<br>
<br>
Let me only enlight you in a few aspects:<br>
<br>
- It is in most situations NOT better than Necro's soloing abbilities. (Even often not better than Mage's solo abbilities /point AFK EXPERIENCE , heh?)<br>
<br>
- It requires some kind of high skill and decent gear<br>
<br>
